{"tid":1076264,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(光速21撚入)點先贏到最京大學？","createTime":"2019-03-24T17:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T08:10:55.000Z","uid":164090,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"aad6bddc382b0b665b3baae9cdc233914b108d2f","tid":1076264,"uid":164090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T17:08:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://img.komicolle.org/2016-12/14825430631635.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.komicolle.org%2F2016-12%2F14825430631635.png&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6QHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=837bf0e3\" target=\"_blank\">http://img.komicolle.org/2016-12/14825430631635.png</a><br />\n<br />\n最京大學：蛭魔、阿含、赤羽、大和、鷹、十文字、番場、一休<br />\n基本上集齊哂各個位置既S-A級既角色，仲要有最強戰略家：蛭魔妖一 (泥門以弱勝強既關鍵)。<br />\n<br />\n依個陣容到底可以點破？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19783025fc640f0a26d1d62ee70b5b76de356604","tid":1076264,"uid":164090,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T17:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.komicolle.org/2016-12/14825430631635.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.komicolle.org%2F2016-12%2F14825430631635.png&h=c6b32737&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eff5276abfe9428f15583f4606f487af9c2ea984","tid":1076264,"uid":58618,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T17:18:13.000Z","msg":"番場邊保護到蛭魔"},{"pid":"a6d8fad6a854044a7225b374334b692c2f656ccc","tid":1076264,"uid":137808,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T17:28:12.000Z","msg":"靠栗田/峨王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce6cd216e96540623a0a99d2a7341f3b77617bc","tid":1076264,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T00:13:34.000Z","msg":"突破4.1入4.0就得"},{"pid":"d02a0f73b14d2aedf83be76be6d38df409e77b7c","tid":1076264,"uid":205516,"like":0,"dislike":0,