e5bb7ae28d202518288efce17f61233188","tid":1076264,"uid":114217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:36:33.000Z","msg":"最京大得offensive勁<br />\n番場破壞力不及峨王<br />\n防守不及栗田<br />\n真係要人地拎99分<br />\n佢地拎100分先可以贏<br />\n<br />\n武藏工有QB第二把交椅基德<br />\n東京四大接球員之一鐵馬<br />\n最強破壞力lineman峨王<br />\n加埋傳說中嘅踢球員武藏<br />\n假如其他位置球員都唔錯<br />\n實力可能仲勁過最京大"},{"pid":"dd7bcbdd3d8b4ffb70e5131875521aeef22934a9","tid":1076264,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:54:21.000Z","msg":"你都要諗下<br />\n蛭魔個腦最強<br />\n但都要泥門啲手腳夠強<br />\n甚至係單獨各部份最強<br />\n然後先返返美式足球原點<br />\n力量、速度、戰略<br />\n簡單講霍金最勁個腦，身體能力咁咪一樣收皮<br />\n唔好唔記得泥門次次都係咁樣反cap 返轉頭<br />\n就算打帝黑嗰時，都要等瀨那真正速度上超越大和，接球先會變得有效<br />\n否則門太接球再Max，得1 個人一樣被人封死"},{"pid":"b764cb76a9f16c9c9d5f5904807f79aa3c30e18c","tid":1076264,"uid":141869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b74f0cac19d8c3a0f12a6d6021e48bb52a6bd0b4","tid":1076264,"uid":164090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T00:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.komicolle.org/2016-12/14825430635977.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.komicolle.org%2F2016-12%2F14825430635977.jpg&h=e5355157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.komicolle.org/2016-12/14825430640617.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.komicolle.org%2F2016-12%2F14825430640617.jpg&h=62eb369d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.komicolle.org/2016-12/14825430653852.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.komicolle.org%2F2016-12%2F14825430653852.jpg&h=6b697328&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T02:23:13.000Z","msg":"王城黃金一代咪輸左比阿進佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁都要格硬攞出來講"},{"pid":"8debaadc5bcaa6c4e2a616766246ee86335ea362","tid":1076264,"uid":31991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T02:28:38.000Z","msg":"搵黑豹做交流生"},{"pid":"6ab6adeaf0162